INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('IX0001', 2019, 2, 'P0000007I', '2019-07-18 23:45:45', 'A0000045C', '2018-06-13 10:54:24', 'Everyone was upfront with pricing, they wanted to make me feel as comfortable as possible (massage options in the chair? tvs above you? headphones for the tv? yes please!), and even though I know they"re churning through patients, I never feel rushed out the door if I have questions or concerns.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('IX0001', 2019, 2, 'P0000007I', '2019-07-18 23:45:45', 'A0000039C', '2019-01-09 10:43:24', 'Had them last night. Great morning left overs. The staff is polite and courteous. I love their beef Mongolian. I feel like they bread their chicken too much it is mushy. BUT great place, fast, good, and clean!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('IX0001', 2019, 2, 'P0000007I', '2019-07-18 23:45:45', 'A0000192N', '2018-04-16 08:07:43', 'We plan on making this our home next time we stop in Vegas.  It"s the perfect getaway off the Strip.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('IX0001', 2019, 2, 'P0000007I', '2019-07-18 23:45:45', 'A0000130F', '2018-06-10 02:33:47', 'I swear if the serving size was more this place could be a easy 4 1/2 Stars. My husband and I along with our boys were in SC last weekend for scheduled maintenance on one of our SUV"s and since the appointment was so early we rushed out without breakfast so of course the entire time in the waiting area we were searching for food.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('IX0001', 2019, 2, 'P0000007I', '2019-07-18 23:45:45', 'A0000183O', '2018-11-11 04:46:15', 'He constantly tried to upsell us. Every order placed was followed by a pause, and "Well, you know what would be really good...?" followed by a big description of a more expensive item or an add-on.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('IX0001', 2019, 2, 'P0000007I', '2019-07-18 23:45:45', 'A0000132A', '2018-04-06 23:35:24', 'Came to this place based on yelp reviews and it did not disappoint. Got the chicken wings to start, kao soi with chicken and an dish from the chefs special - Steamed fish coconut curry. Chicken wings were good, especially when hot, the sauce gelatinized as it cooled. Kao soi was the best I"ve ever had, an excellent portion ans the chicken was very tender. The the fish coconut curry was good too, wasn"t much of a curry but was still very flavourful. Service was fast and people were so friendly and kind. Will definitely go back to try other menu items.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('IX0001', 2019, 2, 'P0000007I', '2019-07-18 23:45:45', 'A0000159V', '2019-10-07 23:50:26', 'Also.... the water gets murky after a while.  Do you really want to go in there?  You would be putting yourself at risk for foot fungus or STDs.  If you do decide to go here, you can go in with full-fledged self-confidence because people will flaunt their stretch marks, cellulite, and other goodies.');
